  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a non-stick skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add onion and garlic, sauté for about 3 minutes or until softened.",
    "Stir in smoked paprika, cumin, and black pepper. Cook for another minute.",
    "Purée chickpeas with half of the cilantro using immersion blender or transfer to a blender.",
    "Mix chickpea purée back into skillet with onion mixture.",
